data.description: $10,000 PRICE IMPROVMENT!! Bring your creativity as a wonderful opportunity awaits in the Battle Forest neighborhood in NW Greensboro! This four sided brick ranch is waiting for you to add your personal touches. Beautiful lot with mature trees. Spacious rooms include two living spaces and a formal dining room. Large kitchen with space for a breakfast nook or to add an island. Built in appliances include a gas cooktop and built-in microwave. Storage shed out back is great for all your yard tools and gardening supplies! The partially finished walk-out basement has plenty of room to expand for additional bedrooms and bonus/game rooms. Please see agent only remarks.
